  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539_1",
    "text": "四、生活中的数学问题。",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.08695652173913043,
      0.13206214689265536,
      0.28585707146426786,
      0.1497175141242938
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539_2",
    "text": "1.一种圆柱形通风管，管口直径是10厘米，长1.2米，做100根 这样的通风管，至少需要铁多少平？（得数保留整平 方米）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11494252873563218,
      0.16031073446327684,
      0.6546726636681659,
      0.23587570621468926
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539_5",
    "text": "思路分析：这是求圆柱表面 积在生活中的应用，求做一 个圆柱形铁皮水桶需要多少 平方厘米的铁皮，就是求这个 圆柱形水桶的侧面积十1个 底面积(水桶有底无盖)。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6796601699150425,
      0.2365819209039548,
      0.9135432283858071,
      0.3990112994350282
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539_4",
    "text": "2.个圆柱的侧展开后是个边长为15.7厘的正形。 这个圆柱的表积是多少平厘?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11294352823588207,
      0.3333333333333333,
      0.6536731634182908,
      0.3813559322033898
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539_7",
    "text": "解答：3.14×20²+2×3.14 ×20×50 =7536（平方厘米） ≈7600（平方厘米）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6786606696651675,
      0.4096045197740113,
      0.912543728135932,
      0.5141242937853108
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539_6",
    "text": "3.根长2、底半径是4厘的圆柱形段，把它锯成同样长 的4根圆柱形的段。表积原来增加了多少平厘?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11294352823588207,
      0.5070621468926554,
      0.655672163918041,
      0.5536723163841808
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1539_8",
    "text": "温馨提示：在实际应用中， 使用的材料都要比计算得 出的结果多一些，所以在取 近似值时要应用“进一法” 取值。",
